{"tid":2435292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：接種疫苗的好處大於風險","createTime":"2021-03-06T06:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T07:03:59.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"06115f96db18f59ad6992b96a2aa1bc0b21e764f","tid":2435292,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:38:50.000Z","msg":"食物及衛生局長陳肇始出席本台節目時表示，目前已有20多萬人預約接種內地科興疫苗，當中約7.2萬人已經接種。她說，一名63歲有長期病患和呼吸道病史的男子，接種內地科興新冠疫苗後兩日死亡，令近日平均每日都少了人預約接種，指市民要「諗清楚」、先詢問家庭醫生，都是人之常情和正常。 <br />\n<br />\n陳肇始指，已預約接種疫苗後無按時到場的個案不多，政府日後一旦知道出現個案，就開誠布公，盡量解答市民疑慮。她重申，兩款供港疫苗都獲政府批准緊急使用，專家檢視後亦認為疫苗安全有效，品質符合要求，強調接種疫苗的好處大於風險。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2381812&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=69415177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2381812</a>"},{"pid":"7b8b383750de2ebb895d65b7a4e6d4dfe893b3c4","tid":2435292,"uid":141668,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:39:38.000Z","msg":"真，幫香港清曬啲藍絲廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ca83b9110c03a8cb6022836e6ab4412289db70","tid":2435292,"uid":91897,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:39:59.000Z","msg":"但直到依家我淨係見到兩條老野死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebed60f6e03dcdccbaff0a9ab823d18ee7a71dc","tid":2435292,"uid":76804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:40:37.000Z","msg":"當g那北京都唔建議60歲以上接種科興<br />\n香港班官為左奶共同清貨可以去到幾盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11fb79edcfdb9cd9da485077691bee730c8782f","tid":2435292,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"死完100%唔會中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直頭冇撚曬風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我黨又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7723e586835ffd8bd0733942e9ad26182b55d3","tid":2435292,"uid":200663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:44:16.000Z","msg":"科興採用陰陽隔離方式 使接種者毋須擔心受感染 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成功率 100% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c6549a0c344f79b4c9c5d5db812924b2aebd3a","tid":2435292,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ebed60f6e03dcdccbaff0a9ab823d18ee7a71dc","tid":2435292,"uid":76804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:40:37.000Z","msg":"當g那北京都唔建議60歲以上接種科興<br />\n香港班官為左奶共同清貨可以去到幾盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:44:23.000Z","msg":"然後藍絲會話，快D 批國藥過黎啦"},{"pid":"da8d15854465d0a6c2f5f069f87b1c9521a3381e","tid":2435292,"uid":81052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"主語係咩?<br />\n邊個既好處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3702783c8e71847bb98b3adcc1e6b0313754c3f","tid":2435292,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3ca83b9110c03a8cb6022836e6ab4412289db70","tid":2435292,"uid":91897,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:39:59.000Z","msg":"但直到依家我淨係見到兩條老野死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T06:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hk